owl:Ontology.rdfs:comment: This is a simple ontology about movies, people working in movies and oscars.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: The duration in minutes of the movie. Any one Movie can only ever have one duration (functional).

owl:DatatypeProperty.dc:description: The original title of the movie. It can be in any language. There must be at one and only oneoriginal title.
